sharing some slices of advo kc ganito kasaya rito ^__^ (lalo na sa Multimedia section 😋) we're the official student publication of FEU, but behind the cameras, laptops closed, and pens down, we're also a family in FEU Advocate wAAHH?? 

With or without experience in journalism, welcome kayo lahat! 

REGISTER HERE
https://forms.gle/we4m9zJW1sotS3kw7

Para sa iba pang mga katanungan, maaari kayong makipag-ugnayan kay Jenah Javier sa 0915 092 2160 o magpadala ng email sa feuadvocate.recruitment@gmail.com
